Invocation Name: one hundred squats
des:
Work out with Alexa throughout the week. Once you open the skill, just ask Alexa to start the workout. You can also ask Alexa for your progress. You can run this program as many times throughout the day as you’d like. The objective is to do 20 squats during each 30 second set.
This skill was created using a Skill Blueprint. Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
